| Aspect | Canvas2D | WebGL |
|--------|----------|-------|
| Complexity | Low | High |
| Debugging | Easy | Difficult |
| Performance (100k cells) | Poor | Excellent |
| Performance (raster tiles) | Good | Good |
| Browser support | Universal | Good |

For raster tile overlays, Canvas2D performance is sufficient.

